<section class="oe_container">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
           <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;"><b>Odoo Leave Request Portal User Employee</h2>
           <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
                This module allow you to employee(s) who are not real users of system but portal users / external user and it will allow to create leave request and edit leave request.
          </p>
          <p style="color:CRIMSON;">
                Main Features:
          </p>
          <p style="color:olive;">
            - Allow you to portal user Leave Request.<br>
            - Portal Users who are employee of system but not real users can fill/record Leave Request entry.<br/>
            - If your company using Leave Request application but not purchased real users from Odoo Enterprise then your employee can fill Leave Request as portal users.<br/>
            - No need to create real users in system if you are only using Leave Request module to make leave request entry for your all employees. <br/>
            - So you can create portal users and set it on employee form and employee can use that portal user logged to fill leave request.<br/>
            - Make sure you have set Portal Employee Leave group on portal user form on settings of users.<br/>
            - Fully mobile responsive.<br/>
            - For more details please watch Video or contact us before buy.<br/>
          </p>
    </div>
</section>
